data.description: MLS# 272686 Welcome to this Beautiful Home on a corner lot in the Desirable location of W. Pasco! Upon entering, you’ll appreciate Bright neutral colors with large windows including the bay window from the living room, open kitchen and dining areas with laminate flooring throughout. The free-flowing kitchen with island has a breakfast bar, convenient built-in appliances and plenty of cabinet space. There are 3 bedrooms including the primary suite with a walk-in shower and built-in seats. The fully fenced backyard is great for entertaining and the concrete curbing makes mowing simple. There is plenty of parking from the 2 car garage and open RV parking with pad and 50 amp service hook up. You’ll be saving money each month with the energy efficient solar panels. Nearby amenities include parks, shopping, convenient stores, Fairchild Cinemas movie theater, Gesa Stadium and quick, easy highway access. Hurry and make arrangements to see this Wonderful home while there’s still time!
